{"id":3473,"date":"2018-01-24T23:25:28","date_gmt":"2018-01-25T04:25:28","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/?p=3473"},"modified":"2018-02-03T19:19:08","modified_gmt":"2018-02-04T00:19:08","slug":"warm-clothes-shipped-to-front-lines","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3473","title":{"rendered":"Warm clothes shipped to front lines"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"eams7\" data-offset-key=\"a27pj-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"a27pj-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"a27pj-0-0\">One of the main initiatives of United Help Ukraine is to provide humanitarian aid to Ukrainian defenders at the front lines. <\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"eams7\" data-offset-key=\"8bd16-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"8bd16-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"8bd16-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"eams7\" data-offset-key=\"f8609-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"f8609-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"f8609-0-0\">Due to the very tough living conditions and cold winter weather warm clothes and medical supplies are needed in larger quantities than currently provided by the government. <\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"eams7\" data-offset-key=\"ab3md-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"ab3md-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"ab3md-0-0\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"eams7\" data-offset-key=\"2qokc-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"2qokc-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"2qokc-0-0\">Our &#8220;adopted&#8221; soldier Max (who UHU had been supporting from the time of his injury near Ilovaisk and after his return back to the front lines) asked us to help his unit with warm clothes. With your generous support through donations, we purchased <a href=\"http